description:
A rich library of helpers, services, and base classes for new and 
      existing Windows UWP apps to maximize awesomeness and minimize boilerplate garbage.
      This library has a companion Visual Studio Extension also called "Template 10".
releaseNotes:
Version 1.1.5
      Correcting double navigation.
      Correcting missing back button behavior.
      Correcting PageHeader ellipsis hover foreground.
      Version 1.1.4
      Created for MVA course on T10.
      Version 1.1.3
      Introducing DeviceDispositionBehavior.
      Version 1.1.2
      Async updates to INavagable and Bootstrapper.PrelaunchAsync.
      Version 1.1.1
      Support for 10586 and DeviceUtils and TaskUtils.
      Version 1.0.8
      Introducing StateItems and SessionState.
      Version 1.0.7
      Introducing ModalDialog and Controls.PiePiece.
      Version 1.0.6
      Introducing WeakReference and Controls.CustomTitleBar.
      Version 1.0.5
      Introducing Controls.Resizer.
      Version 1.0.4

title: Template 10 Library for Windows UWP XAML/.NET apps on Windows 10
